text: Male Mollayeva (; born 19 March 1998) is an Azerbaijani footballer who plays as a defender for the Azerbaijan women's national team. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Azerbaijani women's footballers Category:Azerbaijan women's international footballers Category:Russian Women's Football Championship players Category:Kubanochka Krasnodar players Category:Ryazan-VDV players Category:Azerbaijani expatriate footballers Category:Azerbaijani expatriate sportspeople in Russia Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Russia
